.TH "HPC\-COMPOSE\-EVOLVE" "1" "" "hpc\-compose 0.1.39" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
hpc\-compose\-evolve \- Learn specs by progressively evolving a valid compose file
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
hpc\-compose evolve [OPTIONS]
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Run an authoring\-only tutorial that starts from a minimal valid spec and progressively adds services, readiness, failure policy, and multi\-node placement. Each accepted step validates and writes the current spec without submitting a job, preparing images, or running preflight.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB--lesson\fR \fILESSON\fR
Lesson id to run; defaults to progressive\-complexity.
.TP
\fB--list\-lessons\fR
List shipped evolve lessons and exit.
.TP
\fB--describe\-lesson\fR \fILESSON\fR
Describe one evolve lesson and exit.
.TP
\fB--name\fR \fINAME\fR
Application name written into each accepted spec.
.TP
\fB--cache\-dir\fR \fICACHE_DIR\fR
Optional shared cache directory written into each accepted spec.
.TP
\fB--output\fR \fIFILE\fR
Path to the compose file to evolve. Default: compose.yaml.
.TP
\fB--force\fR
Overwrite the output file if it already exists.
.TP
\fB--yes\fR
Accept each step noninteractively; required with \-\-format json.
.TP
\fB--until\fR \fISTEP\fR
Stop after this step id, for example readiness.
.TP
\fB--format\fR \fIFORMAT\fR
Output format. Possible values: text, json.
.TP
\fB--color\fR \fIWHEN\fR
Controls colored output. Default: auto. Possible values: auto, always, never.
.TP
\fB--quiet\fR
Suppress progress indicators and non\-essential labels.
.TP
\fB--profile\fR \fINAME\fR
Profile name to load from .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB--settings\-file\fR \fIPATH\fR
Explicit settings file path; defaults to upward search for .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB-h\fR, \fB--help\fR
Print help (see a summary with '\-h').
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
hpc\-compose evolve
hpc\-compose evolve \-\-list\-lessons
hpc\-compose evolve \-\-describe\-lesson progressive\-complexity
hpc\-compose evolve \-\-output compose.yaml \-\-name my\-app \-\-cache\-dir '<shared\-cache\-dir>'
hpc\-compose evolve \-\-yes \-\-until readiness \-\-format json
.fi
